{"tid":1733083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美白宮官員譴責香港「不合理武力」對待示威者","createTime":"2019-11-18T04:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:35:06.000Z","uid":54800,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"864506ea1b820521036c288a6a823ce93a9d519a","tid":1733083,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:35:56.000Z","msg":"2019-11-18 HKT 11:39<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮一名高級官員譴責香港使用「不合理武力」對待示威者。（港台圖片）<br />\n美國白宮一名高級官員譴責香港使用「不合理武力」對待示威者。（港台圖片）<br />\n美國白宮一名高級官員譴責香港使用「不合理武力」對待示威者，促請各方克制，避免暴力衝突，並進行建設性對話。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，香港警方封鎖理工大學，導致接近兩日的對峙，憂慮會出現流血場面。一名未有具名的官員表示，總統特朗普早前期望北京政府恪守《中英聯合聲明》的承諾，並保障香港的自由、司法制度與民主生活方式。"},{"pid":"0d4b9a8bd1075a22dc02b6b038210a17f5372e66","tid":1733083,"uid":293698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"118ec6412474c827c941bcd3368a1d6a8fdec50a","tid":1733083,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"不具名官員。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果揾到twittet link 又可以煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21920b75ce8ae0aa0a5eaa7c2a3b074faeece4ba","tid":1733083,"uid":266172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:37:50.000Z","msg":"Source? 揾唔到英文版。"},{"pid":"248678166565499ec004ce219bf14d2c7cae2085","tid":1733083,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"口交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做野未？"},{"pid":"02c5c4e511fcd953985015fefff2fa8bf4f23acf","tid":1733083,"uid":266172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"點都好，有出聲就係好事。"},{"pid":"893bf63de8138e23fa33d73dcf9b0045f5993567","tid":1733083,"uid":203697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"美國同中國一樣都係口交部冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/p